Improve runtime by substituting python3 with pypy3 if possible.

To run the IBM Model 1:

python3 ibm_model1.py
python3 align-f1.py data/train.zh-en.out data/train.align

To run the unmodified True Model 1:

python3 true_model1.py
python3 bleu.py data/test.out data/test.en

To run the modified True Model 1:

python3 true_model2.py
python3 bleu.py data/test.mod2.out data/test.en

To test the pre-run True Model 1:

python3 bleu.py data/test.mod.out data/test.en
